{"id":958832175,"question_id":125,"lang":"javascript","lang_name":"JavaScript","time":"1 year, 1 month","timestamp":1685257728,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"77 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/958832175/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Valid Palindrome","memory":"44.3 MB","code":"/**\n * \n * @param {String} char \n * @return {boolean}\n */\nfunction isAlphaNum(char) {\n  let code = char.charCodeAt(0);\n  return (code >= 48 && code <= 57) \n  || (code >= 65 && code <= 90)\n  || (code >= 97 && code <= 122);\n}\n\nfunction toLower(char) {\n  let code = char.charCodeAt(0);\n  \n  if ((code >= 97 && code <= 122) || (code >= 48 && code <= 57)) {\n    return code;\n  } \n\n  return code + 32;\n}\n\n/**\n * Time O(n), Space O(1)\n * @param {string} s\n * @return {boolean}\n */\nfunction isPalindrome(s) {\n  let left = 0;\n  let right = s.length - 1;\n\n  while (left < right) {\n    if (!isAlphaNum(s[left])) {\n      left++;\n    } else if (!isAlphaNum(s[right])) {\n      right--;\n    } else if (toLower(s[left]) === toLower(s[right])) {\n      left++;\n      right--;\n    } else {\n      return false;\n    }\n  }\n\n  return true;\n}\n","compare_result":"","title_slug":"valid-palindrome","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
